				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The {{gtClass:GtRBNamespace}} class models a Smalltalk image's code, and can be used to build a set of code changes. The changes can be built incrementally without modifying the running Smalltalk image. As the changes are being made, you can ask model for its class or method structure. Once the changes have been made, the changes can be inspected to see what code objects were changed. The changes can also be performed. The performed changes can be undone."
			},
