				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "To define a new class you can use the {{gtMethod:GtRBNamespace>>#defineClass:}} method. That method takes a string that is the class definition either in the old style `subclass:instanceVariableNames:classVariableNames:package:` message style or the newer fluid class style using `<<` and cascading messages to that object using messages like `slots:`.  To remove a class, use the {{gtMethod:RBNamespace>>#removeClass:}} or {{gtMethod:RBNamespace>>#removeClassNamed:}} method. "
			},
